name: Aquarium
description:
Aquarium is an interactive NFT.
Relax yourself looking at your fishes.
Everytime the NFT is loaded, a new aquarium with new fishes will appear. Even other exotic animals can appear!
It's made for PC/Mac browsers, but also for Android/IOS.

Art and code by n0t4numb3r
Music by E-Gerät (soundcloud egerat)
